Terrorsaur:






Terrorsaur rolled away from Autofire's shots. He roll to his knees and said 
to Land Mine and Time Bomb: "We could get all the help we can get!" He 
grunted and lifted himself back into the air.

He squawked in his deep voice and fired his optic lasers at Autofire. "That 
was for that shot earlier!" He turned his head down. "Somebody go with 
Megatron!"
